bowyer^#^
SUBTOPIC-ranger^#^
Command: bowyer

SYNOPSIS
	Ranger skill

DESCRIPTION
	The bowyer skill enables a ranger to craft a bow, and to be
	able to use it more effectively than other classes.

See also: help ranger, man ranger
